help:
```List of current commands: 

	>mock [text0] ; [text1] 
	 Mock a certain quote from a username 

	>listmemes 
	 Send a DM containing all supported meme pictures 

	>make [Meme Template]; [toptext] ; [bottomtext] 
	 Generate A Meme With Text On Top and Bottom 

	>make [Meme Template] ; [bottomtext] 
	Generate A Meme With Text On The Bottom Only 

	>make [Meme Template] ; [toptext] ; 
	Generate A Meme With Text On The Top Only 

	>search [Meme Template] 
	SHow Meme Picture```
